# Blog Card Thumbnails (4:3 Ratio)

Place thumbnail images for blog cards in this folder.

## Image Specifications

**Aspect Ratio:** 4:3 (Standard Blog Cards)
**Dimensions:** 800×600px
**Format:** WebP
**Quality:** 80-85%
**Target File Size:** 50-70KB
**Optimization:** Automatic via Vercel CDN (free)

## SEO Requirements (CRITICAL)

### 1. Filename Naming Convention
```
✅ Good Examples:
- 3d-rendering-house-complete-guide-2025.webp
- interior-rendering-photoreal-process.webp
- 3d-product-visualization-tools.webp
- architectural-design-workflow-tips.webp

❌ Bad Examples:
- img1.webp
- thumbnail.webp
- DSC_1234.webp
- untitled.webp
```

**Rules:**
- Use descriptive, keyword-rich names
- Include main topic + year (if relevant)
- Use hyphens (kebab-case), not underscores or spaces
- Keep it under 60 characters
- No special characters or numbers only

### 2. Alt Text (Add to JSON)
```json
{
  "thumbnail": "/blog-images/3d-render/thumbnails/3d-house-rendering-guide.webp",
  "thumbnailAlt": "Photorealistic 3D house rendering showing modern architectural visualization workflow with lighting and materials"
}
```

**Alt Text Best Practices:**
- 125-155 characters (ideal length)
- Describe what's IN the image
- Include primary keyword naturally
- Be specific and descriptive
- Don't start with "Image of..." or "Picture of..."

### 3. Structured Data Support
Thumbnails are automatically included in BlogPosting schema for:
- Google Search rich snippets
- Social media preview cards (Open Graph)
- Google Discover feed
- Image Search SEO

## Vercel CDN Auto-Optimization

**No extra setup needed!** Vercel automatically:
✅ Serves via global CDN (175+ edge locations)
✅ Converts to WebP format (if not already)
✅ Generates responsive sizes (srcset)
✅ Adds lazy loading
✅ Caches globally for fast delivery
✅ 100% FREE on all Vercel plans

**Example Auto-Generated URL:**
```
Your code: <img src="/blog-images/3d-render/thumbnails/thumb.webp" />
         ↓
Vercel serves:
https://teeli.net/_next/image?url=/blog-images/3d-render/thumbnails/thumb.webp&w=800&q=80
```

## Image Creation Tips

### Content Guidelines:
1. **Hero shot** - Main visual from the blog (cropped to 4:3)
2. **Text overlay** (optional) - Blog title or key phrase
3. **Branding** (optional) - Small logo in corner
4. **High contrast** - Ensure text/elements pop on card backgrounds

### Design Tools:
- Figma (recommended)
- Canva Pro
- Photoshop
- Affinity Photo

### Export Settings:
- Width: 800px
- Height: 600px
- Format: WebP
- Quality: 80-85%
- Color Space: sRGB
- Remove metadata (EXIF)

