## Google Image Search Optimization

To rank thumbnails in Google Image Search:

1. ✅ **Descriptive filename** (keywords)
2. ✅ **Detailed alt text** (125-155 chars)
3. ✅ **High quality** (clear, professional)
4. ✅ **Proper dimensions** (800×600 exactly)
5. ✅ **Fast loading** (under 70KB)
6. ✅ **Structured data** (BlogPosting schema)
7. ✅ **Context** (relevant to blog content)
8. ✅ **Unique** (not stock/duplicate images)

